body:
The kokoro part of this change was tested by running a script to copy this branch to an alternative folder during kokoro process.

The build invocation showed that the key can be retrieved:
`ant -f tool/plugin/compile.xml -Didea.product=android-studio -Didea.version=192.6200805 -Dbasedir=/Volumes/BuildData/tmpfs/src/github/flutter-intellij-kokoro2 -Djxbrowser ...<KEY> compile `

comment_data.body: Edit CONTRIBUTING.md to reference this file.

comment_data.body: You should either add a newline here or specify in the instructions that no newline should be added. Everyone's probably going to add one unless told not to.

commit.message: Write jxbrowser key to a file
Retrieve key from jxbrowser properties file
Return empty string if jxbrowser key file doesn't exist
Update contributing for using license key
Use key from resources during manual build
Return empty string if neither file exists
